sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant F as Frontend
    participant API as FastAPI API
    participant W as Worker/Model
    participant S as Storage

    U->>F: Input business description, model, image count
    F->>API: POST request with data
    API->>W: Start async image generation job
    W->>API: Store job (processing or finished)
    API->>S: Upload generated images/prompts
    alt Images Ready
        F->>API: Poll or websocket
        API->>F: Download links (images, zip)
    end
